                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voilà longtemps que je vous aime :\n— L'aveu remonte à dix-huit ans !—\nVous êtes rose, je suis blême,\nJ'ai les hivers, vous les printemps."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Des lilas blancs de cimetière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Près de mes tempes ont fleuri ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "J'aurai bientôt la touffe entière",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Pour ombrager mon front flétri.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Des lilas blancs de cimetière\nPrès de mes tempes ont fleuri ;\nJ'aurai bientôt la touffe entière\nPour ombrager mon front flétri."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Mon soleil pâli qui décline",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Va disparaître à l'horizon,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Et sur la funèbre colline",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Je vois ma dernière maison.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Mon soleil pâli qui décline\nVa disparaître à l'horizon,\nEt sur la funèbre colline\nJe vois ma dernière maison."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! que de votre lèvre il tombe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Sur ma lèvre un tardif baiser,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Pour que je puisse dans ma tombe,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Le cœur tranquille, reposer !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Oh ! que de votre lèvre il tombe\nSur ma lèvre un tardif baiser,\nPour que je puisse dans ma tombe,\nLe cœur tranquille, reposer !"
        }
    ],
